# ── Experiment outputs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 생성된 시각화·학습 곡선·plot (각 챕터)
# Ch1: Forward closed-form 검증 · noise schedule 비교 · posterior 시각화
# Ch2: ELBO 분해 항별 trajectory · L_simple vs L_vlb 비교 · improved DDPM ablation
# Ch3: NCSN multi-scale Langevin · VP-SDE/VE-SDE trajectory · score 시각화
# Ch4: DDIM vs DDPM step 수 비교 · probability flow ODE · DPM-Solver
# Ch5: CFG scale sweep (w = 0, 3, 7, 15) · classifier guidance trajectory
# Ch6: VAE latent 시각화 · UNet vs DiT scaling · MM-DiT attention map
# Ch7: Consistency Model 1-step · Rectified Flow trajectory · distillation curve
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.svg
*.pdf
*.gif
*.mp4
*.webm
*.webp

